# 🔍 Codex Switcher — Full Code Review & Analysis

## Project Overview

| Item | Detail |
|------|--------|
| **Tujuan** | GUI desktop (EXE) untuk mengganti model AI di `~/.codex/config.toml` tanpa edit manual |
| **Tech Stack** | Electron 28 + Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS (single-file SPA) |
| **API** | 9Router via `https://api.tokito.xyz/v1` |
| **Target Files** | `C:\Users\HP\.codex\config.toml` & `C:\Users\HP\.codex\auth.json` |
| **Build** | `electron-builder` → NSIS installer (.exe) |
| **Source** | Generated by Claude AI, extracted from ZIP |

