## 🔬 Deep Dive: Issue #8 — Wasted fetch-models

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[main.js: fetch-models handler] -->|"Exists but..."| B[preload.js: fetchModels exposed]
    B -->|"Used ONLY in"| C[testConnection function]
    C -->|"Only counts models"| D["Display: '54 model tersedia'"]
    
    E[index.html: MODELS array] -->|"Hardcoded 54 items"| F[renderModels grid]
    
    style A fill:#ff5f57,color:#fff
    style E fill:#ff5f57,color:#fff
```

`fetch-models` **sudah bisa fetch real-time model list** dari API, tapi hasilnya hanya dipakai untuk test connection counter. Model grid tetap pakai hardcoded array.

